'''eSIM'''，又名'''嵌入式SIM'''（{{lang|en|embedded-SIM}}），是一种直接嵌入[[设备|设备]]（焊接在[[PCB板|PCB板]]上）的可编程[[SIM卡|SIM卡]]。使用eSIM的[[手機|手機]]、[[穿戴式裝置|穿戴式裝置]]、[[車載裝置|車載裝置]]及未來[[物聯網|物聯網]]等設備可以無需配有SIM卡卡槽，用户不用插入實體SIM卡就能開通[[移动网络运营商|移动网络运营商]]提供的電信服務<ref>{{Cite web|title=eUICC – The Future for SIM Technology|url=https://podm2m.com/euicc-future-sim-technology/|date=2019-07-05|work=PodM2M|access-date=2021-03-01|archive-date=2019-08-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190829155231/https://podm2m.com/euicc-future-sim-technology/}}</ref>，當更換移动网络运营商時，运营商根据用户的更換请求，通過網絡推送SIM配置文件至用戶设备<ref>{{Cite web|title=政策放行，eSIM就会变得越来越好了吗？|url=https://www.eet-china.com/news/202101221348.html|author=電子工程專輯|access-date=2021-03-01|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225042204/https://www.eet-china.com/news/202101221348.html}}</ref>。
==歷史==
2015年的[[三星Gear_S2|三星Gear S2]][[智能手表|智能手表]]是首款能成功使用eSIM的商業化设备。ESIM標準的第一版于2016年3月发布，第二版于2016年11月发布。苹果在其Apple Watch Series 3及以后的产品中加入了eSIM功能。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.computerworld.com/article/3314537/mobile-wireless/apple-watch-series-4-a-review.html|title=Apple Watch Series 4: A review|last=Evans|first=Jonny|work=Computerworld|access-date=2018-11-09|language=en|archive-date=2018-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181109112208/https://www.computerworld.com/article/3314537/mobile-wireless/apple-watch-series-4-a-review.html}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.macworld.co.uk/feature/iphone/what-is-esim-3683732/|title=Until now, all iPhones have been single SIM, but with eSIM you can have two phone numbers.|last=Martin|first=Jim|work=Macworld UK|access-date=2018-11-09|language=en-GB|archive-date=2018-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181109112126/https://www.macworld.co.uk/feature/iphone/what-is-esim-3683732/}}</ref>此外，他们从iPad Pro（第三代）开始发布的每一台iPad都支持eSIM。苹果还在iPhone XS、iPhone XS Max、iPhone XR和后来的双卡双待产品中加入了eSIM功能。iPhone上若要使用eSIM需要升級到iOS 12.1或更高版本<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.esimreviews.com/which-iphone-models-have-esim-support/|title=Which iPhone models have eSIM support?|website=eSIM Reviews|language=en|access-date=2020-09-07|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225154036/https://www.esimreviews.com/which-iphone-models-have-esim-support/}}</ref>。
==iSIM==
與eSIM相似，但將功能整合到單晶片當中，而非獨立的晶片。可以節省電路板的空間並簡化排線。<ref>{{Cite web|title=一表了解 SIM、 eSIM 與 iSIM|url=https://www.inside.com.tw/amparticle/19065-what-are-sim-esim-and-isim|access-date=2022-02-09|archive-date=2022-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220209113500/https://www.inside.com.tw/amparticle/19065-what-are-sim-esim-and-isim}}</ref>。

